edu.snu.coral.common.ir.vertex

Class MetricCollectionBarrierVertex<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.snu.coral.common.dag.Vertex
      • edu.snu.coral.common.ir.vertex.IRVertex
        • edu.snu.coral.common.ir.vertex.MetricCollectionBarrierVertex<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the metric data.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class MetricCollectionBarrierVertex<T>
extends IRVertex
    IRVertex that collects statistics to send them to the optimizer for dynamic optimization. This class is generated in the DAG through {edu.snu.coral.compiler.optimizer.pass.compiletime.composite.DataSkewCompositePass}.
